videos.description: Ariel Atkins makes a fancy pass to a wide-open Brooke McCarty for a 3.
videos.headline: Texas' McCarty drains an open 3-pointer

videos.description: UConn's Katie Lou Samuelson drains a three to end the 1st quarter.
videos.headline: UConn's Samuelson swishes trey to beat the buzzer

videos.description: Texas' Lashann Higgs finds a cutting Jatarie White for the transition layup.
videos.headline: Great ball movement creates a layup for Texas

videos.description: UConn's Gabby Williams finds Napheesa Collier underneath for the layup to beat the buzzer before halftime.
videos.headline: UConn takes the lead before halftime

videos.description: Texas' Ariel Atkins comes away with the steal and gets the jumper to fall.
videos.headline: Atkins does it all for Texas

videos.description: UConn's Gabby Williams drops a nifty dime to Katie Lou Samuelson who finishes the layup.
videos.headline: UConn's Williams makes an incredible pass to Samuelson for the layup

videos.description: Texas' Brooke McCarty drives to the basket and beats the shot clock to bring Texas within one.
videos.headline: Texas' McCarty makes the clutch scoop layup

videos.description: UConn's Crystal Dangerfield finds Azura Stevens inside to put the Huskies up by 5.
videos.headline: UConn's Dangerfield lobs to Stevens for the layup

videos.description: UConn coach Geno Auriemma talks about how his team battled to defeat Texas, 75-71.
videos.headline: Geno is happy of his team's effort

videos.description: Katie Lou Samuelson leads the No. 1 Huskies with 19 points in a 75-71 win over the No. 9 Longhorns to improve to 16-0.
videos.headline: UConn survives road test against Texas
